---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — gpulse"
  description="Privacy Policy for the gpulse GPU monitoring tool and gpulse.ai website. gpulse collects zero user data from the CLI tool."
>
  <section class="px-4 pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">

      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
      <nav class="mb-8" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="text-sm text-muted transition-colors hover:text-cyan">
          &larr; Back to Home
        </a>
      </nav>

      <!-- Page header -->
      <header class="mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-muted text-lg">
          Effective Date: <time datetime="2026-03-21">March 21, 2026</time>
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="space-y-12 text-muted leading-relaxed">

        <!-- 1. The Short Version -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">1. The Short Version</h2>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-white">The gpulse CLI collects zero data.</strong> No telemetry, no analytics, no crash reports, no network calls. All GPU monitoring data stays on your machine and is never transmitted anywhere.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            The only data we collect is what you voluntarily give us: your email address if you join our waitlist or download list. The Website uses cookieless analytics that cannot identify you. That is the entirety of our data collection.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 2. What the CLI Does NOT Collect -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">2. What the CLI Does NOT Collect</h2>
          <p>
            gpulse runs entirely on your machine. It does not:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-3">
            <li>Transmit telemetry, usage data, or analytics;</li>
            <li>Send crash reports or error logs to any server;</li>
            <li>Collect personal information, hardware fingerprints, or system identifiers;</li>
            <li>Phone home, check for updates, or contact gpulse.ai servers.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            The only optional network feature is the Prometheus metrics endpoint, which you must explicitly enable. It runs locally and exposes data only to services you configure.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 3. Website Analytics -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">3. Website Analytics</h2>
          <p>
            gpulse.ai uses <strong class="text-white">Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong>, which is cookieless and privacy-respecting. It:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-3">
            <li>Uses no cookies or client-side storage;</li>
            <li>Collects no personally identifiable information;</li>
            <li>Does not track users across sessions or websites;</li>
            <li>Provides only aggregated data (page views, referrers, country-level geography).</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            We do not use Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, advertising trackers, or any other third-party tracking scripts.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 4. Email Collection -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">4. Email Collection</h2>
          <p>
            We collect your email address <strong class="text-white">only</strong> if you voluntarily provide it (waitlist signup or download verification). We use it for:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-3">
            <li>Product updates and release announcements;</li>
            <li>Security notices;</li>
            <li>Beta invitations and early access;</li>
            <li>Download verification links.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            <strong class="text-white">We will never sell, share, or trade your email address.</strong> You can unsubscribe at any time.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            <strong class="text-white">Legal basis (GDPR):</strong> Consent under Article 6(1)(a). You may withdraw consent at any time by unsubscribing or contacting us.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 5. Cookies -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">5. Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            gpulse.ai does not use cookies. Cloudflare Web Analytics operates entirely at the edge without any client-side storage. No cookie consent banner is needed because there are no cookies.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 6. Data Storage and Retention -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">6. Data Storage and Retention</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Email addresses</strong> are stored in Cloudflare Workers KV, encrypted at rest. Retained until you unsubscribe or request deletion.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Download logs</strong> (platform type and timestamp only) are retained for one year, then deleted.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Web analytics</strong> are aggregated by Cloudflare with no individual records retained beyond 30 days.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">GPU data</strong> is never stored by us. No database, server, or cloud service receives your GPU metrics.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- 7. Data Processors -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">7. Data Processors</h2>
          <p>
            We use two third-party services:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-3">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Cloudflare</strong> — hosting, CDN, cookieless analytics, Workers KV for email storage. <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" class="text-cyan hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Resend</strong> — transactional email delivery. <a href="https://resend.com/legal/privacy-policy" class="text-cyan hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Neither service has access to your GPU data, because no GPU data is ever transmitted. These services process only email addresses and aggregated web analytics.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 8. Security -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">8. Security</h2>
          <p>
            We protect the limited data we hold with:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-3">
            <li>Encryption at rest for stored email addresses;</li>
            <li>HTTPS/TLS on all Website connections;</li>
            <li>No passwords stored (there are no user accounts);</li>
            <li>Restricted, authenticated access to backend systems.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            No system is perfectly secure. We implement industry-standard practices but cannot guarantee absolute security.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 9. Your Rights (GDPR) -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">9. Your Rights Under GDPR</h2>
          <p>
            If you are in the European Economic Area, you have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-3">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Access</strong> the personal data we hold about you;</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Rectify</strong> inaccurate data;</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Erase</strong> your data ("right to be forgotten") — processed within 30 days;</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Port</strong> your data in a machine-readable format;</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Withdraw consent</strong> for email communications at any time;</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Lodge a complaint</strong> with your local data protection authority.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            <strong class="text-white">Lawful bases:</strong> Consent (Article 6(1)(a)) for email; legitimate interest (Article 6(1)(f)) for aggregated analytics.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            <strong class="text-white">Data controller:</strong> Karthik Kirubakaran. Contact: <a href="mailto:legal@gpulse.ai" class="text-cyan hover:underline">legal@gpulse.ai</a>.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            <strong class="text-white">International transfers:</strong> Data may be processed in the United States via Cloudflare infrastructure. Cloudflare participates in the EU-U.S. Data Privacy Framework.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 10. Your Rights Under CCPA -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">10. Your Rights Under CCPA</h2>
          <p>
            If you are a California resident:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-3">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Right to know</strong> — you may request what personal information we have collected.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Right to delete</strong> — you may request deletion of your personal information.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">No sale of data</strong> — we do not sell personal information and never have.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">No discrimination</strong> — we will not treat you differently for exercising these rights.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            To exercise your rights, email <a href="mailto:legal@gpulse.ai" class="text-cyan hover:underline">legal@gpulse.ai</a>. We will respond within 45 days.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 11. Children -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">11. Children</h2>
          <p>
            gpulse is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, contact us and we will delete it promptly.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 12. Changes -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">12. Changes</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this policy. Changes will be posted here with a revised effective date. Material changes will be communicated via email. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 13. Contact -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">13. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions or requests about your data:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-none space-y-2 mt-3">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Privacy and legal:</strong> <a href="mailto:legal@gpulse.ai" class="text-cyan hover:underline">legal@gpulse.ai</a></li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">General:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@gpulse.ai" class="text-cyan hover:underline">info@gpulse.ai</a></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            We respond to all privacy requests within 30 days.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
